sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant CF as Cloud Functions
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth
    participant DB as Realtime Database
    participant GM as Google Maps

    Note over B,GM: Game Creation

    B->>CF: login({ username })
    CF->>Auth: createCustomToken(uid)
    Auth-->>CF: token
    CF-->>B: { token, uid }
    B->>CF: createGame(username)
    CF->>DB: Set game (5 rounds from location pool)
    CF-->>B: { roomId, token }
    B->>DB: listenGameChanges(roomId)

    Note over B,GM: Player Joins

    B->>CF: joinGame(roomId, username)
    CF->>DB: Add player to game
    DB-->>B: onValue (lobby update)

    Note over B,GM: Round (x5)

    B->>CF: startGame(roomId)
    CF->>DB: status=playing, roundStartedAt=now
    DB-->>B: onValue (round data)
    B->>GM: Street View iframe(lat, lng)
    B->>CF: submitGuess(roomId, round, code)
    CF->>CF: Score = correct ? 1000 + timeBonus : 0
    CF->>DB: Update guess + cumulative score
    DB-->>B: onValue (leaderboard update)
    B->>CF: nextRound(roomId)
    CF->>DB: Reveal answer, advance round

    Note over B,GM: Game Over (after round 5)

    CF->>DB: status=finished
    DB-->>B: onValue (final scores)
